If u get only sound & no picture, u need to install more codecs, divx etc codecs, i recommend this package, includes all:

And that seeding question, u can make ur own torrents of ur files(with torrentmaker) if u like and seed those, but also, when u download those movies & tv series, u can seed those, while u download & after that.. Just make sure, u dont remove that whatever downloading, until share rate is at least 2.0, wich means u have seeded it fully to 2 other persons.. More u seed, bigger share rate = more peoples have got it cos u seeded.
In ur bit torrent client, u can set up upload rate, depending on ur connection speed.
